## Background and requirements:
Ivida Cleaning is a home and commercial cleaning service business. They need a website to inform potential clients. Their main selling point is that they use eco-friendly cleaning products and their excellent training.
- schedule consultation button
- contact us (info@ividacleaning.com)
- about us
- employment opportunities
- our vision (eco friendly, quality control)
- pricing page/transparency
- pages: contact info, transparency, eco friendly

